nodes.label: message
nodes.text: Hi Mr Person1, The test is a Dexa Bone Density Test. This is not a blood test it is a test to see how strong your bones are. I will ask our Clinical Secretary to schedule this and she will call you with the date and time. This test usually takes MM/DD/YYYY to get an appointment which is fine it is not an urgent t est. Let me know if I can help you with anything else.
